Title: Dog Food
Description:
<Dog whines as best as a lion seal can, feebly lifting one flipper toward his massive jaws.

He's hungry.

The Shelf of Mazu is covered in rockshell makrura that should make a fine meal for him.>
ObjectivesText: Help Dog to eat the remains of 10 Rockshell Snapclaws.
CompletionText: <This has got to be the most pathetic lion seal you've ever seen.>
RewardText: <Dog licks his chops happily, looking satisfied.>
